public List<Feature> extract(JCas jCas,
                             Annotation focusAnnotation)
                      throws UnsupportedOperationException
Extract features from the Annotation using the sub-extractors. The parameters are passed on as they are.

Specified by:
extract in interface SimpleFeatureExtractor
Parameters:
jCas -
focusAnnotation -
Returns:
the combined list of features generated by the sub-extractors. If name was set in the constructor, the top-level context of all features will have that as their name.
